oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Penny DeHaven at the Kalkaska Hi School Gym (16291)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: DeHaven, Penny; Roberts, Kenny; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing a Country Music Spectactular featuring Penny DeHaven and Kenny Roberts with Buzz Rider, Jaye Lombard, Michigan Hayride Gang, John Rottman, Jack Ripley, Road Masters, and Billy Adams at the Kalkaska High School Gym on April 26. Poster features metal photoplates of Penny DeHaven and Kenny Roberts. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/20556.
